  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim to evaluate the bone structure by Dexa-scan, extreme CT and bone markers before and
      one year after treatment for a thyroid functional disorder
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The aim to evaluate the bone structure by Dexa-scan, extreme CT and bone markers before and
      one year after treatment for a thyroid functional disorder. Women with hyper- og
      hypothyroidism are included and undergo usual treatment. Patients are stratified into 10
      different groups.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
